tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE complex_analytics (
    id INT,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    location VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE large_datasets (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name TEXT,
    date_added DATE,
    size DECIMAL,
    status BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE analytics_tasks (
    task_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    task_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    status BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE queries_history (
    query_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    query_text TEXT,
    execution_date TIMESTAMP,
    duration INT,
    result_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE data_sources (
    source_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    source_name TEXT,
    source_type TEXT,
    connection_string TEXT,
    date_created DATE
)

CREATE TABLE analytics_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    task_id INT,
    query_id INT,
    result_data TEXT,
    result_date DATE
)
